I'm using crm search API to search deals,accoounts and contacts. I want to search deals which are modified in last 3 days. I found that it can be done by sending filters like,
"filterGroups": [
{
"filters": [
{
"propertyName":"hs_lastmodifieddate",
"value": "2023-10-30T05:37:06.923Z",
"operator": "GT"
}
]
But the problem here is the value, I want it to be dynamic like LAST_N_DAYS:3 in salesforce.
Something like
"filterGroups": [
{
"filters": [
{
"propertyName":"hs_lastmodifieddate",
"value": "LAST_N_DAYS:3",
"operator": "GT"
}
]
and return deals modified in last 3 days.
Is there a HubSpot documentation for this requirement.
Can anyone help me with this?
